p.e:
BEING A NEWCOMER:
It was very strange being on a social VR game.
Granted this wasn't my first time since i had been
on VRCHAT already but I lacked the confidence 
to say anything so to say I didn't feel like I fitted
in is a simple way to put it.
Anyland had a lot of people who actually wanted
to help and talk to me which made me feel a
lot more confident and actually want to stay.
